{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Zen Rage</strong> is a playful nod to the 1990s classic <i>Desktop Destroyer</i>, reimagined with a fresh, chaotic twist.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With <strong>Zen Rage</strong>, you can digitally demolish any image\u2014whether it's a <strong>screenshot</strong> of your current screen, one of the dozen included <strong>template images</strong>, or any image from your hard drive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">But the most fun? <strong>Screenshots.</strong> Bind Zen Rage to a keyboard shortcut, and whenever you're playing a game or dealing with an annoying screen (like a &quot;You died&quot; or &quot;game over&quot; message), just press the shortcut. Zen Rage will instantly take a screenshot, load it, and let you unleash your rage with an arsenal of destructive tools.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Wield the <strong>chainsaw</strong> to slice through the image, shatter your stress with the <strong>hammer</strong>, or fire a <strong>machine gun</strong> barrage. Unleash <strong>digital ants</strong> or electrify the screen with the <strong>Tesla-Coil gun</strong>. The tools at your disposal bring chaos and creativity to your digital destruction spree.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Feeling overwhelmed? Grab the <strong>Zen Rake</strong> to restore balance, paint over your worries with the <strong>paint roller</strong>, or wash it all away with the <strong>water hose</strong>. And when you're ready to start fresh, use the <strong>rubber eraser</strong> to return your image to its original state.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Zen Rage</strong> is your virtual stress ball, offering cathartic relief through the fun of pixelated destruction. Whether it's a quick 5-minute stress buster or a longer session of mayhem, Zen Rage is there to help you blow off steam. Just remember to take breaks and recharge your zen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>PSA</strong>: No ants were harmed in the making of this game.</p>","